dataBase.sentence: Well my dog recently passed away...
Geez I think Global Warming is real...
All my plants died and I'm actually sad...
I wish I was a worm honestly...
Why do we have to kill all these trees?
I think I'm afraid of kittens...
Mushrooms puzzle me so much, man...
Why are there so much types of fishes?
Cute pets kind of disgust me...
Nature is lame but also, so interesting?
